{
  "page": "House Wensington",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Wensington</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Wensington.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Wensington.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f0/House_Wensington.svg/250px-House_Wensington.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f0/House_Wensington.svg/375px-House_Wensington.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f0/House_Wensington.svg/500px-House_Wensington.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"width:100%;min-width:300px;position:relative;z-index:100;border:0 grey solid;margin-top:-3em;margin-bottom:1em;\"><div style=\"display: table; width: calc(100% - 80px); height: 28px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px; margin: 0px auto 0px; padding: 0;border:0; position: relative; border-collapse:collapse; text-align: center; font-family: &#39;Uncial Antiqua&#39;; color: #000; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #007 0%, #007 15%, #ea0 15%, #ea0 85%, #007 85%);\">\n  <div style=\"display:table-cell; vertical-align: middle; padding: 4px; clip-path: polygon(2px 2px, calc(100% - 2px) 2px, calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), 2px calc(100% - 2px)); background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00c 0%, #00c 15%, #fd0 15%, #fd0 85%, #00c 85%);\">Sound The Charge</div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -3; left: -42px; clip-path: polygon(calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), 5px calc(100% - 2px), calc(25% + 3px) 50%, 5px 2px, calc(100% - 2px) 2px, 75% 50%, calc(100% - 2px) calc(100% - 2px), calc(100% - 2px) 5px, calc(75% + 3px) 50%); background: #00c;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -4; left: -42px; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%, 25% 50%); background: #007;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -3; right: -42px; clip-path: polygon(2px calc(100% - 2px), calc(100% - 5px) calc(100% - 2px), calc(75% - 3px) 50%, calc(100% - 5px) 2px, 2px 2px, 25% 50%, 2px calc(100% - 2px), 2px 5px, calc(25% - 3px) 50%); background: #00c;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top: -14px; width: 56px; height: 28px; z-index: -4; right: -42px; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 75% 50%, 100% 100%, 0% 100%); background: #007;\"></div></div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\nTwo golden trumpets crossed on blue, a gold chief with three black stags<br />(<i>Azure, two trumpets saltirewise or, on a chief of the second three stags sable</i>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nUnknown</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlord</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\">House Baratheon</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Wensington</b> is a noble house from the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>. According to semi-canon sources, their arms are two <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">golden</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Trumpet\" title=\"Trumpet\">trumpets</a> crossed on blue, a gold chief with three black stags.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Their motto is \"Sound The Charge\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#House_Wensington_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Wensington at the end of the third century</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Wensington&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>As the upper part of the Wensington coat of arms shows the stag of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\">House Baratheon</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a>, the house may have been founded by a Baratheon or Durrandon.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Wensington&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Wensington&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The Wensington banners are seen at the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> during <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>'s expedition to help the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Thus, most likely the Wensingtons declared first for <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a>, then for Stannis, and some or all of the house remained loyal after the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Wensington_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House Wensington at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Wensington&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Wensington at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The known Wensingtons during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> are: \n</p>\n<ul><li>no member has appeared yet.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Wensington&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_75\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 75\">Chapter 75</a>, Samwell IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel. Heraldry: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Houses/8/\">Houses from the Stormlands</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel. <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Mottoes/\">House Mottoes</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:le